precis:
Regulations Amending the FAMILY SUPPORT ORDERS AND AGREEMENTS GARNISHMENT
REGULATIONS which drop the requirement to provide the Minister with copies
of support orders or agreements and prescribe a 20-day period within which
the Minister must notify a debtor that he has been served with a summons.
